{"by":"JR1427","id":47776139,"kids":[47776169,47778192],"parent":47773812,"text":"A central package cooldown is not really any different to individual cooldowns.<p>The main reason for the cooldown is so security companies can find the issues, not that unwitting victims will find them.<p>One problem of the central cooldown is that it restricts the choice to be able to consume a package immediately, and some people might think that a problem.","time":1776241159,"type":"comment"}